Don't you want to be a famous singer?

196
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:44,400
Don't want to be someone like those dancing on TV, an idol or something?

197
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:47,500
Don't become one of those. Wearing makeup, acting effeminate

198
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:52,700
and always saying "Hello" and "Goodbye." I'm telling you. That's not allowed.

199
00:12:52,700 --> 00:12:57,500
What? I want to study music production. Who says I want to be an idol?

200
00:12:57,500 --> 00:13:01,700
But with your character, you really don't fit. Do whatever you like.

201
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:07,600
Okay, enough of that. Just tell me right now. What's your plan?

202
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:12,500
