Let's talk about it tomorrow. It's a quite tiring trip all the way here.

498
00:33:07,619 --> 00:33:11,919
Look at your son. Shouldn't I say that to him? Even tomorrow?

499
00:33:11,919 --> 00:33:14,319
Tiring? Who isn't tired?

500
00:33:14,319 --> 00:33:16,919
I performed four surgeries today. Am I not tired?

501
00:33:16,919 --> 00:33:19,879
Say it nicely. Don't be harsh.

502
00:33:19,879 --> 00:33:25,059
I'm too good-tempered and have spoiled them like this. Not a single one listens.

503
00:33:25,059 --> 00:33:27,279
Then what else do you want me to do?

504
00:33:27,279 --> 00:33:29,699
I listened to you, so I got into a top high school,

505
00:33:29,699 --> 00:33:34,979
took tutoring classes, and gave up singing.

506
00:33:34,979 --> 00:33:37,779
I can only sleep five hours a day.

507
00:33:37,779 --> 00:33:41,499
And I have to skip rope 1,000 times. You force me to eat so much food.

508
00:33:41,499 --> 00:33:45,739
I'm like a robot living by your orders, and what do you want me to do?

509
00:33:45,739 --> 00:33:49,879
- What are you saying? 
 - Am I your only son? Can you stop always focusing on me alone?

510
00:33:49,879 --> 00:33:52,079
- Come back! 
 - Old Lin.

511
00:33:52,079 --> 00:33:54,539
- Brat. 
 - Dad, don't get anxious.

512
00:33:54,539 --> 00:33:56,859
Are you rebelling?

513
00:33:58,000 --> 00:34:00,460
Brat.

514
00:34:02,119 --> 00:34:05,139
Xiao Ye has grown up. Why not talk to him nicely?

515
00:34:05,139 --> 00:34:06,559
You shut up.

516
00:34:06,559 --> 00:34:10,379
Look at what kind of example you've set for him.

517
00:34:10,379 --> 00:34:13,099
He learned it from you.

518
00:34:13,099 --> 00:34:16,179
Do you think you're all grown up and independent now?

519
00:34:16,179 --> 00:34:19,419
Let me tell you. You are not grown up yet.

520
00:34:23,518 --> 00:34:26,099
Don't you already have a job?

521
00:34:26,099 --> 00:34:31,499
From now on, rely on yourself. Don't come to me for money anymore.

522
00:34:33,159 --> 00:34:34,679
Am I wrong?

523
00:34:34,679 --> 00:34:37,019
Starting tomorrow, you keep an eye on him.

524
00:34:37,019 --> 00:34:39,099
He mustn't go anywhere.

525
00:34:39,099 --> 00:34:41,518
Let's see.

526
00:34:41,518 --> 00:34:46,358
Listen, Lin Ye. If you don't attend a medical school, you'll repeat the year.

527
00:35:07,159 --> 00:35:09,259
 Finally back. 

528
00:35:09,259 --> 00:35:12,979
- The smell of the home is just different. It smells comfortable. 
 - Comfortable.

529
00:35:12,979 --> 00:35:16,319
The hospital really made me feel suffocated. I smell like disinfectant.

530
00:35:16,319 --> 00:35:18,559
But you can't take a bath.

531
00:35:18,559 --> 00:35:20,559
Wouldn't that make me stink?

532
00:35:20,559 --> 00:35:24,199
I'll get you some hot water to wipe your body with.

533
00:35:24,199 --> 00:35:26,119
Later, go lie down in the room.

534
00:35:26,119 --> 00:35:28,959
Take off those dirty clothes. I will wash them for you.

535
00:35:28,959 --> 00:35:31,959
Lying down again? I've been lying for so long.

536
00:35:31,959 --> 00:35:34,199
My body will go to waste.

537
00:35:34,199 --> 00:35:37,439
The doctor told you to lie down. What did he tell you?

538
00:35:37,439 --> 00:35:39,839
After coming back, you need to pay attention to your health.

539
00:35:39,839 --> 00:35:42,299
You need to be careful with all three meals a day.

540
00:35:42,299 --> 00:35:44,639
Your diet should be lighter.

541
00:35:44,639 --> 00:35:46,479
And what else?

542
00:35:46,479 --> 00:35:50,479
Each week, you must do 150 minutes of aerobic exercise.

543
00:35:50,479 --> 00:35:53,579
You mustn't drink alcohol anymore.

544
00:35:53,579 --> 00:35:56,799
I'm talking to you. You can't drink alcohol anymore.

545
00:35:56,799 --> 00:35:59,739
- All right, I won't drink. 
 - You have to monitor your blood pressure every day.

546
00:35:59,739 --> 00:36:02,479
Even slight high pressure is unacceptable.

547
00:36:02,479 --> 00:36:05,119
If that's the case, how am I supposed to live?

548
00:36:05,119 --> 00:36:07,399
Life will be so dull.

549
00:36:07,399 --> 00:36:12,119
To live a happier life, you have to listen to the doctor, right?

550
00:36:12,119 --> 00:36:14,019
Isn't that so?

551
00:36:20,299 --> 00:36:23,679
Xiao Tuo. Come have breakfast.

552
00:36:38,379 --> 00:36:42,099
Mom, don't you think this is too strict?

553
00:36:42,099 --> 00:36:46,259
Xiao Ye is almost 18 years old, but he doesn't even have freedom.

554
00:36:47,879 --> 00:36:50,319
He's forced to study every day by you.

555
00:36:50,319 --> 00:36:53,299
His personality has changed now. It will lead to psychological problems.

556
00:36:53,299 --> 00:36:56,399
Which parent doesn't force their child to study?

557
00:36:56,399 --> 00:37:00,079
Do those children get into Tsinghua or Peking University without any effort?

558
00:37:00,079 --> 00:37:04,339
If one can't get into those, does that mean they don't have a life?

559
00:37:08,559 --> 00:37:12,639
Did you instill these thoughts into Xiao Ye?

560
00:37:12,639 --> 00:37:16,479
Xiao Ye isn't stupid. He has his own thoughts.

561
00:37:17,419 --> 00:37:20,099
What kind of thoughts can a child have?

562
00:37:20,099 --> 00:37:23,799
Mom, he's nearly 18. He's an adult now.

563
00:37:23,799 --> 00:37:25,559
He is still a student.

564
00:37:25,559 --> 00:37:28,859
Does being a student mean one can't have their own thoughts?

565
00:37:32,639 --> 00:37:35,399
Do you want Xiao Ye to end up like you,

566
00:37:35,399 --> 00:37:39,759
attending an ordinary university, not being able to find a job after graduating,

567
00:37:39,759 --> 00:37:43,020
and having to ask us for money to rent a place?

568
00:37:43,020 --> 00:37:46,900
Lin Tuo, do you think your life is good now?

569
00:37:46,900 --> 00:37:52,479
If you had listened to us back then and became a medical student, you would work at our hospital after graduation.

570
00:37:52,479 --> 00:37:54,839
We paved the way for you.

571
00:37:54,839 --> 00:37:59,279
How come you can't understand we were doing it for your own good?

572
00:37:59,279 --> 00:38:03,399
Mom, that's your and Dad's life, not ours.

573
00:38:03,399 --> 00:38:05,259
Let me tell you, Lin Tuo.

574
00:38:05,259 --> 00:38:09,079
Xiao Ye cannot repeat your mistake. Do you know?

575
00:38:09,079 --> 00:38:11,899
Could you please not influence him?

576
00:38:11,899 --> 00:38:15,579
Leave him to prepare for the exam. He has to attend a medical university.

577
00:38:16,159 --> 00:38:17,979
I'm off to work.

578
00:38:17,979 --> 00:38:20,179
I'll go back today.

579
00:38:22,439 --> 00:38:25,659
Say goodbye to your grandfather before you leave.

580
00:38:34,899 --> 00:38:37,199
You got scolded, right?

581
00:38:37,199 --> 00:38:39,319
I almost got beaten up.

582
00:38:40,379 --> 00:38:45,639
I had expected that. Your dad is even more stubborn than I am.

583
00:38:45,639 --> 00:38:49,619
What century is this already? He is still using this method to educate children?

584
00:38:50,619 --> 00:38:53,859
Anyway, I am free. I'll stay in Chongqing.

585
00:38:53,859 --> 00:38:55,639
But what about Xiao Ye?

586
00:38:55,639 --> 00:38:59,419
He doesn't want to go to a medical university.

587
00:38:59,419 --> 00:39:02,459
He wants to go to a music academy, right?

588
