Just a glance tells me exactly what you think.

592
00:39:15,919 --> 00:39:19,299
Back in the day, my dad didn't want me to become a carpenter.

593
00:39:19,299 --> 00:39:22,779
He wanted me to be an electrician and take over his work at the factory.

594
00:39:22,779 --> 00:39:24,759
I refused.

595
