I left home for six years just because of this.

596
00:39:27,799 --> 00:39:31,619
Your mom didn't listen either. She insisted on being a medical student with your dad.

597
00:39:31,619 --> 00:39:36,159
Your grandma wanted her to be a teacher. But she didn't listen.

598
00:39:37,719 --> 00:39:41,719
As parents, we always want to pave a path for our children.

599
00:39:41,719 --> 00:39:44,619
They don't realize children have their own paths.

600
00:39:44,619 --> 00:39:49,339
One has to make their way step by step.

601
