It's not easy to make a living on your own, and you have a girlfriend.

606
00:40:12,899 --> 00:40:16,539
Spend it frugally. But don't let her suffer.

607
00:40:22,479 --> 00:40:26,679
When I'm settled, I'll bring you over. We'll live together.

608
00:40:26,679 --> 00:40:28,739
I'll be waiting.

609
00:40:29,919 --> 00:40:31,839
Thank you, Grandpa.

