It was of no use.

613
00:41:08,899 --> 00:41:11,679
I don't know how to help you.

614
00:41:11,679 --> 00:41:14,259
I can't change our parents' minds.

615
00:41:15,719 --> 00:41:19,839
Does one have to rank first and get into a top university to have a life?

616
00:41:21,459 --> 00:41:25,259
Is one only considered successful when they become a doctor?

617
00:41:27,660 --> 00:41:29,617
I don't know.

